net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base

Class Mapper<C,I,O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base.ClassFieldMapper<C>
      • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base.Mapper<C,I,O>
  • Type Parameters:
    C - the object type of which this maps a field, a.k.a the instance type
    I - The type of the class's mapped field, a.k.a. the instance field type or internal type
    O - The JDBC-level type of the mapped field, a.k.a. the external type or JDBC type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DesMapper<I,O>, PsSetter<O>, RsGetter<O>, SerMapper<I,O>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComposedMapper

    public abstract class Mapper<C,I,O>
extends ClassFieldMapper<C>
implements SerMapper<I,O>, RsGetter<O>, PsSetter<O>, DesMapper<I,O>
    A type-safe mapper for a specific field of a given class.
